<li role="presentation"><a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Arch%20Bone%20Jt%20Surg"[jour]' lang="en" class="usa-link" role="menuitem">Search in PubMed</a></li>
<li role="presentation"><a href='https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog?term="Arch%20Bone%20Jt%20Surg"[Title%20Abbreviation]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem">View in NLM Catalog</a></li>
